# Keep host build artifacts out of the Docker build context. Without this, `COPY . .`
# leaks local bin/obj (and their project.assets.json) into the image, where they collide
# with the container's own `dotnet restore` and fail publish with NETSDK1064.
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/out/
**/publish/

# VCS / IDE / OS noise
.git/
.gitignore
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
**/.DS_Store

# Docs & local tooling not needed to build the images
*.md
docs/
.claude/

# Never ship local secrets / env overrides
**/appsettings.*.local.json
**/*.user
